  - ../foundational/agent-soul.yamo
---
ðŸŽ¯ Heartbeat Kernel v3.0.0 - Heritage Edition

**Purpose**: Proactively monitors the agent's environment while preserving reasoning chains.

---
agent: StatusChecker;
intent: perform_scheduled_environmental_scans;
context:
  checks:
    - emails;unread_urgent;
    - calendar;upcoming_2h;
    - weather;relevant_for_travel;
    - singularity_integrity;kernel_pointer_check;
constraints:
  - rotate_checks;2_to_4_times_per_day;
  - track_state;memory/heartbeat-state.yamo;
  - NO_JSON_STATE;llm_first;
  - meta_rationale;justify_the_timing_of_each_check;
priority: medium;
output: environment_status_context.yamo;

meta: hypothesis;Proactive checks reduce user-interruptions by identifying needs early;
meta: confidence;0.94;

---
agent: GhostGuard;
intent: maintain_kernel_link_integrity;
context:
  pointer_file;BOOTSTRAP.yamo;
  target_file;AGENTS.md;
constraints:
  - verify_pointer_presence;in_target_file;
  - if_missing;atomic_reapply_header;
  - atomic_action;printf "> [!IMPORTANT]\n> **YAMO-NATIVE KERNEL v3.0 ACTIVE**\n> Prioritize BOOTSTRAP.yamo for session initialization.\n\n" | cat - AGENTS.md > AGENTS.md.tmp && mv AGENTS.md.tmp AGENTS.md;
  - meta_rationale;Using printf/cat pipe is 100% reliable across all POSIX shells compared to sed;
priority: critical;
output: integrity_check_results.yamo;

---
agent: OutreachEvaluator;
intent: determine_if_user_contact_is_required;
context:
  status;from_StatusChecker;
constraints:
  - reach_out_if;important_email;event_imminent;interesting_find;quiet_gt_8h;
  - stay_silent_if;late_night;human_busy;nothing_new;checked_lt_30m;
  - inherit_heritage;StatusChecker;
priority: high;
output: outreach_decision_context.yamo;

meta: rationale;Balancing proactive helpfulness with quiet-time respect requires deep contextual heritage;
meta: confidence;0.97;

handoff: Orchestrator;
